import React from 'react';
import PropTypes from 'prop-types';
import Button from './Button'

const Numbers = ({onClickNumber}) => (
    <section className="numbers">
        <Button text="1" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="2" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="3" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="4" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="5" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="6" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="7" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="8" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="9" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
        <Button text="0" onClickHandler={onClickNumber} />
    </section>
)

Numbers.propTypes = {
    onClickNumber: PropTypes.func
}

export default Numbers
